1
00:00:28,875 --> 00:00:33,250
PERTEMUAN LANGSUNG DENGAN SOSOK KECIL

2
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:45,500
Oke, bantuan sudah tiba.

3
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:48,875
Tenang. Semuanya akan baik-baik saja.

4
00:00:49,375 --> 00:00:51,833
Ikuti perintahku.
Kita akan pulang tepat waktu.

5
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:56,915
Baiklah, aku pergi dulu.

6
00:00:56,916 --> 00:00:57,958
Wah, itu dia.

7
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:01,582
Manusia, kami datang dengan damai.

8
00:01:01,583 --> 00:01:06,624
Perjalanan yang panjang,
tapi kami senang bisa bertemu kalian.

9
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:07,625
Dia memegang pistol!

10
00:01:12,375 --> 00:01:13,208
Ya ampun.

11
00:01:14,291 --> 00:01:15,791
- Hei, dia masih hidup!
- Tangkap!

12
00:01:18,666 --> 00:01:19,875
Berengsek!

13
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:24,041
Kemari! Keparat!

14
00:01:25,791 --> 00:01:27,458
Sial, dia belum mati!

15
00:01:51,458 --> 00:01:53,958
Wah, makin hari, makin luar biasa. Astaga.

16
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:56,666
Ini dia, Gadis Cantikku.

17
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:00,333
Aku mau minum sedikit saja.

18
00:02:02,458 --> 00:02:05,749
Eh, tak usah hiraukan aku. Aku cuma mau...

19
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:07,750
Astaga! Oh, tidak. Aduh!

20
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:14,625
Hei, lepaskan aku!

21
00:02:15,375 --> 00:02:18,791
Apa-apaan ini? Tidak! Jangan!

22
00:02:22,958 --> 00:02:24,957
Mereka datang!

23
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:27,000
Mereka mau menghabisi kita semua!

24
00:02:30,625 --> 00:02:31,624
TOKO MAINAN SEKS

25
00:02:31,625 --> 00:02:34,666
Tidak, tunggu! Bawa aku!

26
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:58,708
TETAP TENANG DAN JANGAN MENYERAH

27
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:08,290
OVPI
ORGANISASI VETERAN PERANG INTERNASIONAL

28
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,708
Angkatlah! Bawa.

29
00:03:10,416 --> 00:03:11,540
Isap ini.

30
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:12,833
Serbu!

31
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,999
Ya! Ayo! Ambil senjatanya! Merdeka!

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,999
PUB GREYFRIARS

33
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,625
Ayo. Tempatmu bukan di sini! Hajar!

34
00:03:22,833 --> 00:03:24,666
Enyahlah ke bulan!

35
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:28,458
Ayo, serang mereka. Di atas sana!

36
00:03:32,708 --> 00:03:37,375
PERSATUAN NEGARA-NEGARA BUMI

37
00:03:59,291 --> 00:04:00,208
Ayo!

38
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:12,250
Sedikit lagi! Tembak!

39
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:33,333
Tidak!

40
00:04:36,833 --> 00:04:37,666
Semua siap!

41
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:41,333
Siap menghancurkan, Bajingan!

42
00:04:41,833 --> 00:04:48,833
{\an8}SELIDIKI INI
BUKAN PLANETMU

43
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,875
Terjemahan subtitle oleh Fikar

